Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:21.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}自分の過去に囚われ迷って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:26.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}そうじゃないよと　言い聞かせて　全てを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:31.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}自由に操れるかなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:34.30,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}分からないよと　空は霞んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:36.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}正解はどこ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:42.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}僕の手のひらに　残る大事なもの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:46.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}忘れない記憶　何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:51.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}君を守り抜くと叫んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:57.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}巻き戻しの中　掴んだ愛は　そう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:59.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}離しはしないから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:04.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}散りばめた想い　今一度きりの願いへ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:09.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}次への僕に　託したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:14.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}いつかの約束　光の道しるべになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:25.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}誓いをさあ　君のため　最期まで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:30.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}涙さえ力に変えてきっと　描いていた望む未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:33.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}繋ぐよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:21.66,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}无法摆脱自己过去的束缚  迷失了前进方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:26.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}还自欺述说那并不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:31.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}不知道这些是否能自由控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:34.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}天色为何又如此朦胧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:36.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}答案又在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:42.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}双手还残留着有什么很重要的事尚未完成的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:46.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}这段记忆将尘封于心  永久保存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:51.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}誓要将你保护到底的决心已化作言语放声呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:57.03,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}回放逝去的倒带  把对你永恒的挚爱捧在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:59.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}定不会轻易放手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.49,0:02:04.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}这是最后一次请求  将这散落一地的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:09.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}托付给未来的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:14.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}曾经的约定  化作黎明的灯塔指引我前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:25.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}我发誓将为了你支撑到最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:30.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}连泪水也化作力量  一定会将心中描绘的所期待的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:33.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}与现实衔接
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:56.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:58.58,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:04.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:06.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:15.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}狂った時計　刻む命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.93,0:23:19.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.81,0:23:23.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:28.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:35.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.91,0:23:37.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:39.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:45.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:52.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:54.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:56.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.10,0:24:01.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:06.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:10.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:13.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:15.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.87,0:24:19.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:21.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:23.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:56.33,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.41,0:22:58.58,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:04.13,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.21,0:23:06.17,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:15.85,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失准的时钟 记录着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.93,0:23:19.73,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}散落满地的记忆之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.81,0:23:23.61,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:28.57,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看 却是那么轻易
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:35.87,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.91,0:23:37.12,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望能与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.16,0:23:39.20,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.25,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰 我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:45.75,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不再失去曾经拥有的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:52.59,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我忘却自己的过去 重新开始旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.68,0:23:54.80,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不 请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:56.89,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望 不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.10,0:24:01.31,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愿那让你苦不堪言的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:06.90,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}会迎来完结的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:10.53,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我却要目送你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:13.95,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:15.99,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.12,0:24:17.08,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.87,0:24:19.66,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:21.83,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:23.25,EDCNCHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手迈进
